{"article_id":"91H20dCcYuDf9yWL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The Associated Press does n't question the Justice Department 's right","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"to have seized two months ' worth of its phone records ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"the organization 's president and CEO Gary Pruitt said Sunday on `` Face the Nation .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"'' It was the methodology","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"- `` so sweeping , so secretively , so abusively and harassingly overbroad , ''","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"he said -","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"that breached the Constitution .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"As part of its criminal investigation","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"into who may have leaked information","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"contained in a May 7 , 2012 , AP story about a foiled terror plot in Yemen ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"the department `` issued a secret subpoena for the phone toll records for 21 AP phone lines","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"and these were phones lines for reporters , direct lines , cell phones , home phones but also the office numbers , ''","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Pruitt explained .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"`` So over 100 , approximately a hundred journalists used these telephone lines as part of newsgathering","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and over the course of the two months of the records","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"that they swept up ,","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"thousands upon thousands of newsgathering calls were made . `` ... Under their own rules , they are required to narrow this request as narrowly as possible","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"so as to not tread upon the First Amendment , ''","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"he went on .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"`` And yet they had a broad , sweeping collection ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"and they did it secretly .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Their rules require them to come to us first","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"but in this case they did n't ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"claiming an exception ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"if they had","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"it would have posed a substantial threat to their investigation .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"But they have not explained","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"why it would","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"and we ca n't understand","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"why it would . ''","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Pruitt said","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"the AP acted `` responsibly ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"'' holding the story for five days","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"upon receiving guidance from the intelligence community","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"that it posed a national security risk .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"It was important for the American public to know about the CIA operation","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that thwarted an al Qaeda plot","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"to detonate a bomb aboard a U.S.-bound airplane ,","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"he continued ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"because `` the Department of Homeland security were telling the American public","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"that there was no credible evidence of a terrorist plot","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"related to the anniversary of the killing Of Osama bin Laden . ''","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"That characterization was `` misleading . ''","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"A call from a Washington , D.C. district attorney last week notified the AP of the subpoenaed phone records ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Pruitt said .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Since then ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"he added ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"`` officials","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"that would normally talk to us ,","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"and people","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"we talk to in the normal course of newsgathering ,","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"are already saying","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"they 're a little reluctant to talk to us ;","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"they fear","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"that they will be monitored by the government .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"`` ... The government has no business having control over all ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"monitoring all of this newsgathering information from the Associated Press , ''","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"he continued .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"`` And","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"if they restrict that apparatus ,","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"you 're right","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"- the people of the United States will only know what the government wants them to know","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"and that 's not what the framers of the Constitution had in mind","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"when they wrote the First Amendment . ''","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":133,"left":0,"right":132,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":69,"right":131,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":72,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":71,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":70,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":96,"right":129,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":85,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":77,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":74,"right":76,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":8,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":75,